title: [Icemule, Fear Alley]
description: A few low buildings mix with the odd tall kiosk in this quiet yet bustling back alley.  Along the wall, some local wag has scratched the image of a giant rat chasing a young halfling adventurer out of the well into the ice covering the wall.
